WEBVTT

1
00:01:10,416 --> 00:01:12,000
Kau bersamanya?

2
00:01:12,625 --> 00:01:14,250
Bagus? Ayolah.

3
00:01:14,916 --> 00:01:15,916
Ayo.

4
00:01:24,875 --> 00:01:25,875
Sial.

5
00:03:11,250 --> 00:03:12,625
Aku menyerah.

6
00:03:18,791 --> 00:03:21,958
Pengutang berengsek sepertimu
tak akan bayar tanpa kekerasan.

7
00:03:23,666 --> 00:03:26,875
Aku menyerah.
Tolong ampuni aku sekali ini.

8
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:30,458
Aku akan berusaha melunasinya.

9
00:03:30,541 --> 00:03:31,875
Lepaskan aku kali ini saja.

10
00:03:36,833 --> 00:03:39,791
Jika lain kali tak bayar,
kujadikan kau makanan anjing.

11
00:04:01,083 --> 00:04:08,041
THE DEBT COLLECTOR

12
00:04:11,541 --> 00:04:16,375
{\an8}TEGANGAN TINGGI
BERBAHAYA

13
00:04:16,458 --> 00:04:20,250
{\an8}ZONA 3
KHUSUS PERSONEL

14
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:26,583
Punya utang itu penderitaan.

15
00:04:26,666 --> 00:04:27,666
10 TAHUN KEMUDIAN

16
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:31,000
Dalam Dhamma, namanya "utang karma".

17
00:04:32,250 --> 00:04:33,625
Karma baik dan buruk

18
00:04:34,375 --> 00:04:38,625
mengarah ke kebahagiaan dan penderitaan.

19
00:04:39,541 --> 00:04:42,291
Kalian semua di sini

20
00:04:42,375 --> 00:04:45,708
untuk melunasi utang karma
yang kalian punya.

21
00:04:46,291 --> 00:04:47,625
Penjara adalah kurungan…

22
00:04:48,708 --> 00:04:50,416
untuk menghukum,

23
00:04:51,833 --> 00:04:54,583
tapi juga memperbaiki diri kalian

24
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:59,708
demi merasakan hasil karma kalian.

25
00:05:01,250 --> 00:05:03,375
Hukuman kalian hampir selesai.

26
00:05:04,625 --> 00:05:07,000
Kalian harus melunasi utang karma.

27
00:05:08,041 --> 00:05:09,583
Kalian harus memulai hidup baru,

28
00:05:10,583 --> 00:05:13,500
bersikap baik,

29
00:05:14,416 --> 00:05:17,250
<i>dan berkontribusi kepada masyarakat.</i>

30
00:05:17,333 --> 00:05:18,833
<i>Amin.</i>

31
00:05:18,916 --> 00:05:21,458
<i>Amin.</i>

32
00:05:43,958 --> 00:05:48,416
PENJARA PROVINSI

33
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,125
Biksu di mana?

34
00:06:31,208 --> 00:06:33,000
Di gua di atas bukit.

35
00:06:33,083 --> 00:06:35,000
<i>Naiklah. Lewat sini.</i>

36
00:07:14,583 --> 00:07:16,750
Rupanya kau.

37
00:07:18,666 --> 00:07:19,708
Bagaimana kau kemari?

38
00:07:21,583 --> 00:07:23,458
Kau sudah makan?

39
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,208
Aku berjalan ke sini.

40
00:07:28,833 --> 00:07:32,250
Aku mau memberi hormat kepadamu.

41
00:07:35,416 --> 00:07:37,333
Sekarang kau bebas dari penderitaan.

42
00:07:39,083 --> 00:07:42,625
Setelah ini, kau harus mulai hidup baru.

43
00:07:44,791 --> 00:07:47,625
Sudah pikirkan
bagaimana kau akan mencari nafkah?

44
00:07:50,708 --> 00:07:51,708
Belum.

45
00:07:57,375 --> 00:07:59,708
Kau bisa mengemudi?

46
00:08:03,041 --> 00:08:05,541
- Ya, bisa.
- Baiklah. Bagus.

47
00:08:06,208 --> 00:08:09,666
Muridku sedang mencari sopir
untuk mengantar barang.

48
00:08:11,833 --> 00:08:12,833
Apa kau tertarik?

49
00:08:14,291 --> 00:08:16,291
Aku akan memintanya menerimamu.

50
00:09:12,958 --> 00:09:14,916
AGUSTUS 2005

51
00:10:00,875 --> 00:10:02,083
Kiriman paket, Pak.

52
00:10:09,583 --> 00:10:10,791
Paket.

53
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:24,916
SOPIR BURUK:
BAWA KARMA BAIKMU SENDIRI

54
00:10:35,208 --> 00:10:38,166
EKSPRES JAI PETCH

55
00:10:46,458 --> 00:10:48,000
Manisnya.

56
00:10:49,208 --> 00:10:52,958
Ajak dia menemanimu.

57
00:10:53,708 --> 00:10:54,958
Aku tak bisa merawatnya.

58
00:10:57,375 --> 00:10:59,000
Tolong rawat dia.

59
00:11:18,625 --> 00:11:21,041
Silakan. Sampai jumpa besok pagi.

60
00:11:25,458 --> 00:11:26,500
Mau pesan apa?

61
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:31,083
Rebung tumis, telur goreng.

62
00:11:31,166 --> 00:11:32,250
Pakai nasi?

63
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:17,666
Paman.

64
00:12:18,916 --> 00:12:20,125
Uangnya ketinggalan.

65
00:12:22,791 --> 00:12:23,791
Itu untukmu.

66
00:12:26,375 --> 00:12:27,708
Berterima kasih, Nid Noi.

67
00:12:28,625 --> 00:12:29,625
Terima kasih.

68
00:12:31,375 --> 00:12:32,375
Nenek.

69
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,000
Kau simpan saja.

70
00:12:55,166 --> 00:12:56,291
Bagaimana?

71
00:13:09,250 --> 00:13:10,250
Apa ini?

72
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:13,791
Cuma itu yang kupunya. Ambillah.

73
00:13:14,291 --> 00:13:16,458
Jalang! Apa?

74
00:13:16,541 --> 00:13:18,250
Apa-apaan ini?

75
00:13:21,166 --> 00:13:22,166
Sial!

76
00:13:29,375 --> 00:13:31,875
Tolong hentikan. Kau membuatnya takut.

77
00:13:32,458 --> 00:13:33,708
Anak itu takut?

78
00:13:34,666 --> 00:13:36,500
Anak itu takut, Nenek Tua?

79
00:13:37,583 --> 00:13:38,583
Hei!

80
00:13:39,708 --> 00:13:41,041
Jangan ikut campur!

81
00:13:49,333 --> 00:13:51,291
Dasar bodoh. Kau siapa?

82
00:13:51,958 --> 00:13:53,916
Kenapa ikut campur?

83
00:13:57,708 --> 00:13:58,708
Kumohon, Pak.

84
00:14:00,625 --> 00:14:01,708
Jangan sakiti dia.

85
00:14:03,208 --> 00:14:04,958
Berapa utangnya? Kubayarkan.

86
00:14:05,958 --> 00:14:06,958
Maka berikan 10.000.

87
00:14:10,250 --> 00:14:11,250
Cepat.

88
00:14:24,458 --> 00:14:26,875
Cuma ini yang kupunya. Tolong terima.

89
00:14:27,458 --> 00:14:28,458
Hei.

90
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:32,750
Ayo pergi.

91
00:14:38,625 --> 00:14:39,625
Jalan.

92
00:15:04,541 --> 00:15:05,541
Hei.

93
00:15:18,333 --> 00:15:19,333
Hei.

94
00:15:26,541 --> 00:15:27,583
Ini cuma bunganya.

95
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:31,875
Bisnis sedang sepi.

96
00:15:41,083 --> 00:15:43,000
Katamu akan bayar uang mukanya juga.

97
00:15:44,208 --> 00:15:45,458
Jadi…

98
00:15:46,625 --> 00:15:48,625
Kapan dibayar?

99
00:15:49,375 --> 00:15:53,791
Lain kali, bungamu dua kali lipat.

100
00:15:53,875 --> 00:15:54,958
Baik, Pak.

101
00:15:56,708 --> 00:15:57,916
Jangan buat aku repot.

102
00:16:32,708 --> 00:16:34,000
Belok kiri di depan.

103
00:16:59,166 --> 00:17:00,166
Terima kasih.

104
00:17:01,875 --> 00:17:03,625
Masuklah untuk minum air.

105
00:17:07,416 --> 00:17:08,416
Terima kasih.

106
00:17:13,625 --> 00:17:15,000
Ambilkan air untuknya.

107
00:17:33,666 --> 00:17:35,000
Kalian berdua saja?

108
00:17:36,875 --> 00:17:39,583
Ya, cuma aku dan cucuku.

109
00:17:40,625 --> 00:17:41,875
Ibunya meninggalkannya…

110
00:17:41,958 --> 00:17:43,250
NID NOI SAYANG NENEK

111
00:17:44,458 --> 00:17:45,750
…dan pergi begitu saja.

112
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:50,041
Tak meninggalkan uang sama sekali.

113
00:17:52,541 --> 00:17:56,000
Uang hari tuaku
tak cukup untuk membesarkannya.

114
00:17:58,375 --> 00:17:59,708
Aku harus bersusah payah

115
00:18:01,166 --> 00:18:02,250
dan menjual makanan.

116
00:18:06,708 --> 00:18:10,166
Aku tak punya tabungan,
jadi meminjam dari mereka.

117
00:18:14,208 --> 00:18:15,375
Berapa utangmu?

118
00:18:19,208 --> 00:18:20,458
Aku meminjam 30.000 baht…

119
00:18:22,333 --> 00:18:27,208
untuk membeli gerobak
dan lainnya untuk memasak.

120
00:18:30,875 --> 00:18:32,791
Bunganya 1.000 baht per hari.

121
00:18:35,916 --> 00:18:36,958
Lalu entah bagaimana…

122
00:18:43,333 --> 00:18:44,875
utangku jadi melebihi 100.000.

123
00:18:49,666 --> 00:18:52,416
Bagaimana bisa kulunasi?

124
00:19:13,458 --> 00:19:14,458
Terima kasih.

125
00:19:15,458 --> 00:19:17,250
Begitu punya uang, akan kubayar.

126
00:19:18,041 --> 00:19:19,250
Tidak usah.

127
00:19:23,583 --> 00:19:24,583
Ini untukmu.

128
00:19:32,916 --> 00:19:35,208
Semoga Buddha melindungi
orang baik sepertimu.

129
00:19:38,458 --> 00:19:39,458
Terima kasih.

130
00:19:50,791 --> 00:19:53,791
Paman, aku bayar untuk nenekku.

131
00:19:57,875 --> 00:19:58,875
Simpan saja.

132
00:20:11,166 --> 00:20:12,500
Anggap utangmu lunas.

133
00:20:14,291 --> 00:20:15,416
Beri tahu nenekmu.

134
00:20:16,958 --> 00:20:18,541
- Mengerti?
- Paman terluka?

135
00:20:30,208 --> 00:20:32,125
Bentuknya mirip sayap malaikat.

136
00:20:39,333 --> 00:20:41,458
Terima kasih
sudah menyelamatkanku dan Nenek.

137
00:20:45,958 --> 00:20:47,833
Aku sudah bayar, Nek.

138
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,125
Sial!

139
00:21:34,208 --> 00:21:37,583
Pak! Ada yang jatuh.

140
00:21:40,500 --> 00:21:42,250
Kau punya tumor otak

141
00:21:44,125 --> 00:21:48,458
yang menyebabkan kejang,
mual, dan pingsan mendadak.

142
00:21:48,541 --> 00:21:52,250
Kau bisa berhalusinasi
mendengar atau melihat sesuatu.

143
00:21:53,125 --> 00:21:57,458
Tumormu tidak bisa dioperasi.

144
00:21:57,541 --> 00:21:58,791
Terlalu berbahaya.

145
00:21:59,875 --> 00:22:02,541
Kusarankan radioterapi demi kesehatanmu.

146
00:22:08,625 --> 00:22:09,666
Waktuku berapa lama?

147
00:22:11,125 --> 00:22:14,875
Jika kau menjalani radioterapi,
mungkin sekitar setahun.

148
00:22:16,083 --> 00:22:17,125
Jika tidak,

149
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:20,541
mungkin kurang dari sebulan.

150
00:23:21,250 --> 00:23:24,333
Tolong hentikan, kumohon.

151
00:23:24,916 --> 00:23:28,416
Kau memohon apa? Memohon untuk apa?

152
00:23:28,500 --> 00:23:30,208
Uangmu tidak cukup!

153
00:23:31,291 --> 00:23:32,791
Nenek!

154
00:23:39,500 --> 00:23:41,000
Hei! Bocah sialan.

155
00:23:53,750 --> 00:23:55,208
Bajingan.

156
00:24:09,125 --> 00:24:10,125
Sial!

157
00:24:15,875 --> 00:24:17,958
Ayo keroyok dia!

158
00:24:19,041 --> 00:24:20,041
Ayo.

159
00:24:21,958 --> 00:24:23,833
Hei! Polisi datang!

160
00:24:23,916 --> 00:24:25,250
Kak, ada polisi.

161
00:24:25,333 --> 00:24:26,500
- Ayo pergi!
- Ayo.

162
00:24:40,458 --> 00:24:41,458
Ada apa ini?

163
00:24:42,041 --> 00:24:43,875
Geng penagih utang

164
00:24:43,958 --> 00:24:47,708
merusak kios nenek ini
dan pria itu membantunya.

165
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:52,041
Kau mau bagaimana? Mau laporkan?

166
00:24:53,291 --> 00:24:55,958
Aku bisa melaporkan mereka?

167
00:24:56,041 --> 00:24:57,083
Ya.

168
00:24:57,166 --> 00:25:00,291
Pergi saja ke kantor polisi
dan buat laporan.

169
00:25:02,916 --> 00:25:05,166
Sebaiknya kau jadi saksinya.

170
00:25:13,166 --> 00:25:16,458
Kau tak tahu
pinjaman tanpa izin itu ilegal?

171
00:25:17,166 --> 00:25:18,875
Ini dampaknya jika tak bayar.

172
00:25:21,750 --> 00:25:24,041
Jadi, kau mau aku bagaimana?

173
00:25:25,291 --> 00:25:28,083
Mereka berapa orang
saat datang merusak gerobakmu?

174
00:25:28,166 --> 00:25:29,250
Kau ingat orangnya?

175
00:25:29,916 --> 00:25:32,125
Aku ingat. Mereka selalu berempat.

176
00:25:32,750 --> 00:25:36,333
Kau, yang berbaju hitam di belakang.
Lepaskan topimu.

177
00:25:40,208 --> 00:25:42,583
Baju hitam. Hei, kau.

178
00:25:45,041 --> 00:25:46,500
Kubilang lepaskan topimu.

179
00:25:52,208 --> 00:25:53,333
Num, dasar bajingan.

180
00:25:54,708 --> 00:25:56,083
Kapan kau bebas?

181
00:25:57,375 --> 00:25:58,458
Apa yang kau lakukan?

182
00:25:58,541 --> 00:25:59,541
Khem.

183
00:26:00,333 --> 00:26:02,041
Katanya dia saksinya.

184
00:26:02,125 --> 00:26:05,625
Dia menyelamatkannya
dari geng penagih utang.

185
00:26:06,291 --> 00:26:07,416
Aku tak salah dengar?

186
00:26:08,750 --> 00:26:09,750
Nenek.

187
00:26:10,458 --> 00:26:13,708
Apa kau tahu sebenarnya
dia penagih utang yang kejam?

188
00:26:14,958 --> 00:26:17,750
Dia menembak kepala peminjam
dan dipenjara sepuluh tahun.

189
00:26:19,166 --> 00:26:21,750
Kau membohonginya?

190
00:26:21,833 --> 00:26:23,416
Paman Num tak membohongi kami.

191
00:26:23,958 --> 00:26:25,875
Dia membantu kami.

192
00:26:32,458 --> 00:26:34,458
Pastikan buat laporannya, Num.

193
00:26:47,208 --> 00:26:48,583
Aku bisa pergi sendiri.

194
00:26:55,083 --> 00:26:56,166
Tak mau merepotkan.

195
00:26:59,208 --> 00:27:00,333
Bisa kuantar.

196
00:27:02,125 --> 00:27:03,500
Barang bawaanmu banyak.

197
00:27:04,166 --> 00:27:05,416
Tak apa.

198
00:27:06,208 --> 00:27:09,416
Taruh barangku di sini.
Biar aku yang urus.

199
00:27:12,416 --> 00:27:13,416
Aku…

200
00:27:15,125 --> 00:27:17,041
Aku masih mau berbicara ke polisi.

201
00:27:34,916 --> 00:27:36,458
Ambil semua isi di toko ini.

202
00:27:39,500 --> 00:27:42,958
Hei, tunggu. Hei!

203
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:47,500
Aku sudah bayar.

204
00:27:48,250 --> 00:27:49,791
Kau terlambat membayar.

205
00:27:49,875 --> 00:27:50,875
Bunganya naik.

206
00:27:52,416 --> 00:27:53,916
Ini belum setengahnya.

207
00:27:55,583 --> 00:27:57,291
Hei, Kau! Jangan yang itu!

208
00:27:59,291 --> 00:28:00,291
Kutelepon Madam Pin.

209
00:28:05,541 --> 00:28:07,625
Kenapa menelepon ibuku?

210
00:28:09,500 --> 00:28:11,833
Kenapa kau meneleponnya?

211
00:28:12,458 --> 00:28:13,708
Bicara saja kepadaku!

212
00:28:20,708 --> 00:28:23,666
Kau bayar sebanyak apa pun yang kuminta.

213
00:28:24,416 --> 00:28:25,708
Apanya yang sulit dipahami?

214
00:28:25,791 --> 00:28:26,791
Bajingan!

215
00:28:39,583 --> 00:28:42,250
Hei, kalian kenapa?

216
00:28:52,250 --> 00:28:53,250
Ada apa?

217
00:29:21,833 --> 00:29:23,083
Nid Noi, kemari.

218
00:29:26,291 --> 00:29:28,291
Nenek! Buka pintunya!

219
00:29:28,916 --> 00:29:31,250
Kubilang, buka, jalang!

220
00:29:33,208 --> 00:29:34,500
Mana bajingan itu?

221
00:29:38,583 --> 00:29:40,833
Nenek, ayo bicara.

222
00:29:42,500 --> 00:29:44,125
Buka pintu, bicara baik-baik.

223
00:29:50,625 --> 00:29:51,958
Kau tak bisa bayar utang

224
00:29:53,250 --> 00:29:55,208
dan berani melapor ke polisi?

225
00:29:56,041 --> 00:29:58,208
Kau tak tahu polisi ada di pihakku?

226
00:30:01,583 --> 00:30:02,583
Aku tidak tahu.

227
00:30:03,750 --> 00:30:05,208
Polisi itu menyuruhku.

228
00:30:08,208 --> 00:30:09,208
{\an8}Keluar.

229
00:30:11,250 --> 00:30:12,250
{\an8}Kemari.

230
00:30:13,541 --> 00:30:15,166
Kubilang keluar!

231
00:30:15,250 --> 00:30:19,291
Nenek sialan! Kau tak dengar? Dasar bodoh!

232
00:30:19,875 --> 00:30:21,166
Keluar!

233
00:30:32,666 --> 00:30:34,083
Kau tak mau keluar?

234
00:30:45,541 --> 00:30:47,041
{\an8}Maka terkurunglah dan mati.

235
00:30:48,416 --> 00:30:49,416
Nenek sialan.

236
00:31:18,458 --> 00:31:19,708
Kumohon.

237
00:31:21,333 --> 00:31:22,916
Aku menyerah.

238
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:31,000
Ya.

239
00:31:32,291 --> 00:31:33,666
Ambil perekat.

240
00:31:36,541 --> 00:31:39,125
Kubilang, ambil perekatnya, Bodoh.

241
00:31:42,333 --> 00:31:43,208
Ikat dia.

242
00:31:59,375 --> 00:32:00,666
- Tolong!
- Lepaskan aku!

243
00:32:06,208 --> 00:32:09,458
Tolong! Nid Noi!

244
00:32:13,541 --> 00:32:16,416
Tolong!

245
00:32:17,041 --> 00:32:18,333
Nid Noi!

246
00:32:19,083 --> 00:32:22,125
Tolong!

247
00:32:48,958 --> 00:32:50,708
Hei, Nenek tak berjualan hari ini?

248
00:32:57,375 --> 00:32:59,708
<i>Kau tak tahu rumah Nenek Lek terbakar?</i>

249
00:33:15,083 --> 00:33:17,291
<i>Penyelamatnya menemukan jasadnya gosong.</i>

250
00:33:17,875 --> 00:33:19,958
<i>Tangannya diikat ke gerbang besi.</i>

251
00:33:35,916 --> 00:33:38,583
<i>Ada yang melihat mobil Po,</i>
<i>si lintah darat,</i>

252
00:33:39,458 --> 00:33:41,291
