522
01:04:24,583 --> 01:04:27,166
Sialan! Dia monster.

523
01:04:55,208 --> 01:04:58,291
<i>Pusat ke semua unit.</i>
<i>Ada pria misterius yang mirip Num.</i>

524
01:04:58,375 --> 01:05:01,625
<i>Dia mengendarai motor merah dan putih</i>
<i>di persimpangan Ratchadamri,</i>

525
01:05:01,708 --> 01:05:03,583
<i>menuju ke kota. Ganti.</i>

526
01:05:03,666 --> 01:05:04,666
Aku mau pergi.

527
01:05:04,750 --> 01:05:07,041
Hei, tunggu. Hei!

528
