558
01:09:38,208 --> 01:09:39,208
Po!

559
01:10:08,958 --> 01:10:11,041
Empat kilo, sesuai permintaan.

560
01:13:21,625 --> 01:13:24,041
Num.

561
01:13:24,125 --> 01:13:25,125
Maaf.

562
01:13:30,000 --> 01:13:31,250
Utangku empat juta.

563
01:13:34,625 --> 01:13:36,583
Aku bantu pinjaman polisi lain,

564
01:13:38,250 --> 01:13:39,458
