565
01:13:41,083 --> 01:13:42,625
Aku yang harus melunasinya.

566
01:13:46,708 --> 01:13:47,750
Aku sudah habis akal.

567
01:13:49,125 --> 01:13:50,125
Maaf.

568
01:14:01,458 --> 01:14:02,458
Num.

569
