611
01:19:19,791 --> 01:19:22,791
Jika kau bunuh, kubayar 100.000.

612
01:19:26,625 --> 01:19:27,625
Sialan!

613
01:19:40,791 --> 01:19:41,791
Selamat malam, Pak.

614
01:19:50,666 --> 01:19:52,875
Jika ucapanmu benar,

615
01:19:54,333 --> 01:19:55,708
