634
01:21:30,541 --> 01:21:31,958
Kau bisa dipercaya?

635
01:21:38,333 --> 01:21:39,333
Ya, Pak.

636
01:21:40,541 --> 01:21:41,541
Bagus.

637
01:21:43,041 --> 01:21:47,083
Mulai sekarang,
laporkan semua petunjuk cuma kepadaku.

638
01:21:48,041 --> 01:21:50,541
Aku akan urus para pejabat tinggi.

639
01:21:51,833 --> 01:21:52,833
Baik, Pak.

640
01:23:08,541 --> 01:23:10,333
Kenapa kau tak menyelamatkanku?

641
