651
01:26:40,416 --> 01:26:41,458
Omong-omong utang…

652
01:26:42,583 --> 01:26:44,250
Kuil ini berutang kepadaku.

653
01:26:45,875 --> 01:26:49,208
Kuil ini tak akan ada
tanpa uang keluargaku.

654
01:26:52,458 --> 01:26:54,375
Bukannya bersyukur,

655
01:26:55,166 --> 01:26:56,416
kau malah berkhianat.

656
01:26:58,291 --> 01:27:00,916
Sekarang belum terlambat, Po.

657
01:27:04,500 --> 01:27:05,666
Jangan menambah karma…

658
01:27:09,791 --> 01:27:10,791
Hei.

659
01:27:22,625 --> 01:27:24,333
Kurung dia!

660
01:27:44,458 --> 01:27:45,833
Kau ingat ini?

661
01:28:01,375 --> 01:28:02,375
