Hei, Num.

674
01:35:50,458 --> 01:35:52,208
Po, ayo pergi.

675
01:35:55,166 --> 01:35:56,166
Sial!

676
01:36:02,666 --> 01:36:04,750
PENGANTARAN PASIEN DARURAT

677
01:36:04,833 --> 01:36:07,166
Tolong!

678
01:36:11,041 --> 01:36:12,041
Cepat!

679
