Bu, Jod mati.

680
01:36:26,000 --> 01:36:29,375
<i>Jangan pulang.</i>
<i>Bersembunyi dulu di tempat lain.</i>

681
01:36:29,458 --> 01:36:31,708
<i>Begitu rencana kabur siap, Ibu jemput.</i>

682
01:36:31,791 --> 01:36:32,791
Baiklah.

683
01:36:37,541 --> 01:36:38,916
Hei, masuk.

684
01:36:53,958 --> 01:36:54,958
Halo, Inspektur.

685
01:36:55,458 --> 01:36:56,458
<i>Kau di mana?</i>

686
01:36:59,583 --> 01:37:01,208
Kau tahu soal kuil itu, 'kan?

687
01:37:01,291 --> 01:37:02,291
<i>Ya.</i>

688
01:37:02,875 --> 01:37:04,291
<i>Pergi ke rumahku sekarang.</i>

689
01:37:05,000 --> 01:37:06,833
<i>Kita tangkap Madam Pin malam ini.</i>

690
01:37:09,083 --> 01:37:10,083
Ya, Inspektur.

691
01:37:30,083 --> 01:37:31,083
Baiklah.

692
01:37:32,541 --> 01:37:33,541
Ya, Pak.

693
01:37:35,000 --> 01:37:36,375
Kemajuannya bagus.

694
01:37:37,083 --> 01:37:38,916
Aku akan terus kabari.

695
01:37:40,875 --> 01:37:41,875
Ya.

696
01:37:43,791 --> 01:37:44,791
Ya.

697
01:37:54,166 --> 01:37:56,250
Kita diizinkan menangkap Madam Pin.

698
01:38:01,416 --> 01:38:04,916
Anak buahku melaporkan
kau membantu Num kabur.

699
01:38:06,250 --> 01:38:07,250
Kenapa?

700
01:38:12,041 --> 01:38:13,041
Num temanku.

701
