707
01:38:40,250 --> 01:38:41,375
Di rumah sakit.

708
01:38:42,916 --> 01:38:44,083
Yang mana?

709
01:38:52,041 --> 01:38:53,958
Apa-apaan kau?

710
01:38:54,041 --> 01:38:55,041
Bajingan!

711
01:39:01,541 --> 01:39:02,666
Apa-apaan ini?

712
