726
01:46:51,708 --> 01:46:54,416
<i>Halo, Madam Pin. Aku Kong.</i>

727
01:46:55,916 --> 01:46:58,416
<i>Aku tahu kau menyuap Inspektur Tong</i>

728
01:47:00,291 --> 01:47:01,708
