736
01:47:36,250 --> 01:47:38,333
akan kubuat dia mengatakannya.

737
01:47:41,875 --> 01:47:42,916
<i>Baik, akan kukatakan.</i>

738
01:47:44,875 --> 01:47:47,500
<i>Po di gedung terbengkalai</i>
<i>di Khlong Suk. Jangan…</i>

739
01:47:57,541 --> 01:47:58,541
Num.

740
01:47:59,875 --> 01:48:01,000
Kumohon.

741
01:48:03,291 --> 01:48:04,875
Jangan bunuh Po.

742
01:48:11,208 --> 01:48:12,708
Kumohon.

743
01:49:18,708 --> 01:49:19,791
Lepaskan aku.

744
01:54:37,166 --> 01:54:38,166
Kau tak apa-apa?

745
01:54:56,583 --> 01:54:58,333
Berhenti! Mundur.

746
01:54:58,916 --> 01:55:00,708
Berhenti! Mundur!

747
01:55:00,791 --> 01:55:02,416
Mundur! Minggir!

748
01:58:34,666 --> 01:58:36,500
Num. Num, kumohon.

749
01:58:36,583 --> 01:58:39,166
Jangan bunuh aku! Kumohon!

750
01:58:39,250 --> 01:58:41,833
Maafkan aku. Kumohon, Num.

751
01:58:45,208 --> 01:58:47,875
Aku akan menyerahkan diri
dan dipenjara seumur hidup.

752
01:59:16,000 --> 01:59:17,125
Kau berlagak hebat?

753
01:59:28,791 --> 01:59:30,708
Hei!

754
01:59:33,166 --> 01:59:34,166
Kugorok dia!

755
01:59:35,750 --> 01:59:36,916
Lempar senjatanya.

756
01:59:39,708 --> 01:59:40,958
Kubilang lempar!

757
01:59:46,583 --> 01:59:47,583
Kau bercanda?

758
02:00:00,166 --> 02:00:02,583
Apa-apaan kau?

759
02:00:02,666 --> 02:00:04,708
Apa kau sudah gila?

760
02:00:10,000 --> 02:00:12,666
Kuledakkan otakmu, Bajingan!

761
02:00:23,333 --> 02:00:24,166
Berengsek!

762
02:02:18,958 --> 02:02:21,166
Sersan Mayor Sitta Yannaboon,

763
02:02:21,250 --> 02:02:23,541
petugas dari Divisi Investigasi,

764
02:02:23,625 --> 02:02:25,666
Kepolisian Provinsi Phetchaburi,

765
02:02:25,750 --> 02:02:29,458
bertugas dengan keberanian,
dedikasi, dan komitmen tak gentar.

766
02:02:29,541 --> 02:02:31,833
Dia pilar utama kepolisian

767
02:02:31,916 --> 02:02:34,333
dalam membasmi grup kriminal lokal

768
02:02:34,416 --> 02:02:36,875
yang sudah bermasalah
selama bertahun-tahun.

769
02:02:44,375 --> 02:02:45,583
Ya, Pak.

770
02:02:45,666 --> 02:02:47,791
<i>Bagaimana, Polisi Bintang?</i>

771
02:02:47,875 --> 02:02:49,000
<i>Selamat.</i>

772
02:02:50,375 --> 02:02:52,500
<i>Ya, aku cuma menelepon untuk memberitahumu</i>

773
02:02:52,583 --> 02:02:54,750
<i>Inspektur Tong gantung diri di penjara.</i>

774
02:02:54,833 --> 02:02:58,375
<i>Mereka memeriksa, dia dibungkam</i>
<i>atau bunuh diri untuk kabur dari masalah.</i>

775
02:02:59,291 --> 02:03:01,875
<i>Sial. Seharusnya tak begini.</i>

776
02:03:02,458 --> 02:03:05,666
<i>Baiklah, telepon aku saat kau</i>
<i>kembali ke Phetchaburi.</i>

777
02:03:05,750 --> 02:03:07,583
<i>Aku dan timku akan mentraktirmu.</i>

778
02:03:48,750 --> 02:03:50,208
Dari EKG-nya,

779
02:03:50,291 --> 02:03:56,166
kebocoran di katup jantung Nong Ping Ping
sudah sangat menyusut.

780
02:03:56,875 --> 02:04:00,041
Sekarang sudah tak perlu dioperasi.

781
02:04:02,083 --> 02:04:03,083
Terima kasih.

782
02:12:44,000 --> 02:12:46,000
Terjemahan subtitle oleh Sudirman Lius